{"tid":1581710,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[搵人落黎幫拖先] 唔知壞咩 救命","createTime":"2019-09-19T16:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T11:06:06.000Z","uid":254906,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4c61e49ed47315f1c936c6ad6a3cd6028fb87d34","tid":1581710,"uid":254906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:33:54.000Z","msg":"話說我買咗borderlands3黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點知窒到仆街，咁唯有upgrade吓條女啦，買咗新ram u 板。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓我個list先<br />\n<br />\ncpu:  i7-9700F LGA1151 (新買)<br />\n<br />\n媽媽： Gigabyte H310M S2H 2.0 (新買) <br />\n<br />\nram:  ddr4 a-data 16gb (新買)<br />\n<br />\n卡： msi 970<br />\n<br />\nssd:  sandisk 120gb *2<br />\n<br />\nhdd:  wd 1tb<br />\n<br />\n牛牛： sharkoon wpm 700w<br />\n<br />\n (用緊win10 順便重裝埋) <br />\n<br />\n點知唔換由自可，一換完之後問題就黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n換之前最多打機窒吓窒吓，但係都仲叫玩到。<br />\n<br />\n而家換完之後部機就瀨晒野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通就咁用都冇事，不過一run &quot;恆&quot;啲或者打機就會hang機，要reboot先郁得番嗰隻hang。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇夠硬既朋友知係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教練，我想打機呀。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3714e96b10ff721c7a199b5d43fcafcba2c1c60","tid":1581710,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:34:04.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=06193afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"e657a06df28c2960c081b67cebd23ef5c404898c","tid":1581710,"uid":59734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"sharkoon 牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daedcd82adbe098298859a87c6f9d8f15e99e139","tid":1581710,"uid":59734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"同埋borderlands 3 shit performance 係optimize問題"},{"pid":"b3b30900238a465a3382cfbe89f413fcfc59af79","tid":1581710,"uid":254906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"sharkoon好流？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係應該唔關佢事掛 未換 ram u 板 之前都係用緊呢隻牛。 <br />\n<br />\n我開borderlands嗰陣會開到一陣 的確嗰一陣係順過以前好多 但係入到game過多10秒左右就會freeze咗。。。"},{"pid":"a70114f2601f30d9ddfd9cb86e32a40d5e49cd00","tid":1581710,"uid":29985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b463c00111d1a86e07dc238f998b5f67dfdca8","tid":1581710,"uid":254906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a70114f2601f30d9ddfd9cb86e32a40d5e49cd00","tid":1581710,"uid":29985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />